Text: Maltese Capital Management LLC lifted its position in CNB Financial by 72.3% during the 2nd quarter. Maltese Capital Management LLC now owns 207,399 shares of the bank's stock valued at $5,857,000 after acquiring an additional 86,999 shares during the period.
